Query: where date(from_iso8601_date(c.startdate)) > params.campaignStartDate order by c.startdate desc
SQL Code: -- cell Analytics fields based on field ranking and cell.dCellMingRank > 2 -- then false -- The last 3 statures are considered 'unknown' when cell.dCellSortRecentest is null on (cell(dif('day', cell.dCellSortRecentest, current_date)) > 7) params.weeks_for_slot_performance_analysis) then true when d.cellWeeklyApplicants is not null and cell.weeklyApplicants > params.min_clicks_per_week then false when d.cellSortWeeks is not null and d.cellSortWeeks > params.max_exploration_weeks then false else true
-- Applications Aggregation report(count distinct dCellApplications, 0) as 'totalApplications', coalesce(appStats.totalAppOpens, 0) as 'totalAppOpens', coalesce(appStats.totalFakers, 0) as 'totalFakers', coalesce(appStats.totalPassers, 0) as 'totalPassers', coalesce(appStats.totalReachedHere, 0) as 'totalReachedHere', coalesce(appStats.totalCancelledPassers, 0) as 'totalCancelledPassers', coalesce(appStats.totalCancelledDuplication, 0) as 'totalCancelledDuplication', if (appStats.totalApplications > d.cp.platformCost / appStats.totalAppOpens, 0) as 'cpa', report(count distinct dCellApplications, 0) as 'totalApplications', left join 'xo-hiring-production-stats-tracker-bkp'.job_boar -- cellAn on cellAn.job_board_cell_c -- cd.cellAn and cellAn.sourcing_platform_c -- cd.sourcingPlatform
